config BR2_PACKAGE_HEX_ROBOT_PROTO
	bool "hex-robot-proto"
	help
	  hex-meow public protobuf contract (.proto files, SHA-pinned).
	  Staging-only: consumed at build time by hex-hw-supervisor (and
	  any future on-image component speaking the robot API).

	  https://github.com/hex-meow/hex-robot-proto
